  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 874b5e5991c8ddd4c9ddbc996be428fb, type: 3}
  m_Name: RangerRoget
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mail
  sender: rangerroget@yurimail.com
  subject: "DON\u2019T GO OUTSIDE."
  body: "DON\u2019T GO OUTSIDE.\n\nI don\u2019t know what\u2019s going on. A bunch
    of military personnel from that neighboring military site rolled up and they
    rounded us up and locked us up in the ranger station and told us not to leave
    or else.\r\n\nI don\u2019t know what\u2019s going on but I keep hearing gunshots
    and people screaming. Then I looked out the window earlier and I saw this thing.It
    looked human but then its face opened up and it tore off a soldier\u2019s face.
    It\u2019s a mad house out here. Just don\u2019t go outside.\r\n\n-Ranger Roger."
